  talk_03:
    attributes: Npc_TabantaHatago001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 9
      - text: 横渡北方广袤的
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 塔邦挞大雪原
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "后，\n你会看到一个"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 巨大的迷宫
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "。\n不知道是谁，又是何时盖在那里的。\n大人们总说那里很危险，所以不可以接近。"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n某天，我要"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 海罗
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n进去迷宫玩试胆游戏。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 结果这成了我跟
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 海罗
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 最后的回忆。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n那里真的是个危险的地方。\n小孩子就是尽做些胡来的事……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - control:
          kind: raw
          zero:
            four:
              field_1: 0
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: 至今这段回忆仍让我心痛不已。
  talk_06:
    attributes: Npc_TabantaHatago001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "到了这把年纪，\n想起的尽是孩提时代的回忆啊。\n话虽如此，这种边境"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "很少有小孩子。\n我的朋友，也只有"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 海罗
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 和
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 玛莉
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "而已。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 25
      - text: 和
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 海罗
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 在迷宫玩的回忆，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n和"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 玛莉
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 在遗迹玩的回忆……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - control:
          kind: choice
          choice_labels:
            - 2
            - 3
            - 4
          selected_index: 0
          cancel_index: 2
          unknown: 8
  talk_07:
    attributes: Npc_TabantaHatago001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 18
      - text: "你知道在这驿站的东南方\n有座很大的峡谷吗？\n谷底有座很古老很古老的遗迹……\n\n不知是谁，又是何时盖在那里的，\n大人们总说那里很危险，所以不可以接近。\n某天，我和"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 玛莉
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "自称是探险队，\n打算去寻找遗迹。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 然而
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 玛莉
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "却失足从崖上掉下去，\n这成了我们之间的最后回忆……\n小孩子的好奇心\n有时会导致难以挽回的悲剧啊。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: 至今这仍是段令我难过的回忆……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
  talk_08:
    attributes: Npc_TabantaHatago001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 0
      - text: 你还真忙啊。
